Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Philippines election queried
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xpl3
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Feb 1986
US queries organisation of snap election called by Philippines dictatorial President Marcos. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less